  <CE_Settings_EnableSimplifiedAmmo_Desc>TODO</CE_Settings_EnableSimplifiedAmmo_Desc>

	<!-- EN: Right-click ammo selection -->
  <CE_Settings_RightClickAmmoSelect_Title>右键选择弹药</CE_Settings_RightClickAmmoSelect_Title>
	<!-- EN: Right-clicking the reload button brings up the ammo selection menu. -->
  <CE_Settings_RightClickAmmoSelect_Desc>右击装弹按钮以选择弹种。</CE_Settings_RightClickAmmoSelect_Desc>

	<!-- EN: Auto-reload on ammo select -->
  <CE_Settings_AutoReloadOnChangeAmmo_Title>自动重装新选择弹药</CE_Settings_AutoReloadOnChangeAmmo_Title>
	<!-- EN: Pawns will automatically reload when a new ammo type is selected. -->
  <CE_Settings_AutoReloadOnChangeAmmo_Desc>当新的弹种被选择时，人物会自动装填新弹药。</CE_Settings_AutoReloadOnChangeAmmo_Desc>

	<!-- EN: Auto-equip ammo -->
  <CE_Settings_AutoTakeAmmo_Title>自动装备弹药</CE_Settings_AutoTakeAmmo_Title>
	<!-- EN: Pawns without loadouts assigned will automatically pick up ammo for their equipped weapon. -->
  <CE_Settings_AutoTakeAmmo_Desc>未指定装备分组时候，人物会自动拾取适合手中武器的弹药。</CE_Settings_AutoTakeAmmo_Desc>

	<!-- EN: Display weapon caliber -->
  <CE_Settings_ShowCaliberOnGuns_Title>显示武器弹药类型</CE_Settings_ShowCaliberOnGuns_Title>
	<!-- EN: Ammunition-using weapons will have their caliber appended behind their name. -->
  <CE_Settings_ShowCaliberOnGuns_Desc>自动在武器的名字后面加上弹药类型以及口径标准。</CE_Settings_ShowCaliberOnGuns_Desc>

	<!-- EN: Re-use neolithic projectiles -->
  <CE_Settings_ReuseNeolithicProjectiles_Title>可重复使用的石器时代弹药</CE_Settings_ReuseNeolithicProjectiles_Title>
	<!-- EN: Neolithic projectiles will have a chance to drop on the floor on impact. They are automatically forbidden. -->
  <CE_Settings_ReuseNeolithicProjectiles_Desc>石器时代的武器弹药在发射后将会有几率掉落在地上，默认禁止互动。</CE_Settings_ReuseNeolithicProjectiles_Desc>

	<!-- EN: Realistic cook-off -->
  <CE_Settings_RealisticCookOff_Title>弹药爆燃效果</CE_Settings_RealisticCookOff_Title>
	<!-- EN: Ammunition stacks won't spawn damaging projectiles on cooking off. -->
  <CE_Settings_RealisticCookOff_Desc>弹药堆在受热燃烧的时候不会产生随机乱射的效果。</CE_Settings_RealisticCookOff_Desc>

